Please run `npm run build && npm run lint && npm test` before ever committing. If any errors are detected, fix them.

The process consists of:
* Build (TypeScript compilation)
* Lint (ESLint validation)
* Unit Tests (Jest)
* Type Check (TypeScript validation)
* Container builds verification
